      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition, offering a smooth, reliable ride that you can count on for years to come. It has been well cared for and performs beautifully, showing only minor, honest signs of character from its time on the road. It\u2019s the perfect balance of quality and value for anyone seeking a dependable, high-quality vehicle!",
