    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The engine currently struggles to stay running and requires significant mechanical attention, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, and the interior shows heavy wear including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It will likely need to be towed from the lot, as it is not currently reliable for daily driving.",
