      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a refined balance of performance and reliability. This specimen has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our standards of mechanical excellence and aesthetic preservation. Representing a superior value for the discerning driver, it features a sophisticated interior and a robust powertrain designed for long-term service. This is an authoritative choice for those seeking a dependable, high-caliber driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
