      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-cared for over the years. It runs super smooth and is just waiting for someone new to take it on some fun adventures! If you're looking for a reliable, great-looking car that's ready to hit the road, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This unit features a healthy double-VANOS system and crisp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies. The drivetrain is paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced to address common floor-pan fatigue, and the suspension has been refreshed with polyurethane bushings and Bilstein dampers for precise turn-in. While the exterior shows minor road-wear consistent with a well-loved driver, the internal mechanicals are dialed in, and the engine pulls strongly through the entire 8,000 RPM powerband. A turn-key example for the performance-oriented collector.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 32000.0,
